               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="40"/>
                     <title>Prayers and excerpts from the Bible</title>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="1r"/>
                        <title>Prayers of the middle of the night</title>
                        <!-- Cp. BAVet64 f. 4-12 -->
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="7v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT3522Epistle"/> 4:14-5:10</title>
                        <note>
                           The verse <q xml:lang="gez">ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ጥዑመ፡ ስም፡ ዘጸዋዕኮ፡ ለጰውሎስ፡ ጸውዓነ፡ ውስተ፡ ከብካብከ።</q> is added on <locus target="#8v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="9r"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT3507Epistle"/> 5:5-11</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ኦዘለከ፡ ተውህበከ፡ <choice><sic>መራኁተ፡</sic></choice> ዘመንግሥተ፡ <choice><sic>ሰማያተ።</sic></choice> 
                           ኰኵሐ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ አርኅወነ፡ ንባዕ፡ ቤተ፡ መርዓሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፨</q> is added on <locus target="#9v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="9v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1019Actsof"/> 16:30-34</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">ስቡሕ፡ አንተ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ወመንክር፡ ስነ፡ ስብሐቲከ፡</q> is added on <locus target="#10r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1558Matthew"/> 25:1-13</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez"><choice><sic>ርስየነ፡</sic></choice> ድልዋነ፡ ንትቀበል፡ ከመ፡ መርዓዊ፡ በዘይተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ <add place="margin">ጥሉል፡</add></q> 
                           is added on <locus target="#11r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1793Leviti"/> 23:1-8</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">እስመ፡ <choice><sic>ውእቱ፡</sic></choice> ዘወሀበ፡ ሕገ፡ ለሙሴ፡ ሰነብታቲሁ፡ ረሰየ፡ ለክብር፡ ወለውዳሴ፡</q> is added on 
                           <locus target="#11v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                        <locus from="12v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1693John"/> 5:1-18</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ረ<supplied reason="omitted">ስ</supplied>የነ፡ ድልዋነ፡ ከመ፡ ንባዕ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰንበተ፡ ሰበታቲሁ፡ ምስለ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ቅዱሳኒከ፡ ከመ፡ 
                              ንኩን፡ <choice><sic>ጽዋዓነ፡</sic></choice> ለበዓልከ፡</q> is added on <locus target="#14"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                        <locus from="14v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT3516Epistle"/> 15:51-16:2</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez"><supplied reason="omitted">ጥ</supplied>ዑመ፡ ልሳን፡ ምዑዝ፡ ከመ፡ ዕጣን፡ ጳውሎስ፡ መርሐ፡ ዕውራን፡ ዘበጽንፈ፡ ልብስከ፡ 
                              <choice><sic>የሐይው፡</sic></choice> ዱያን፡</q> is added on <locus target="#15"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9">
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT3509Epistle"/> 1:1-5</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ዕፀ፡ አርዝ፡ ኀበ፡ ሙሐዘ፡ ማይ፡ ዘበቈለ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አሕመልመለ።</q> is added on <locus target="#15v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1019Actsof"/> 16:30-34</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">አንቅዕተ፡ ሕግ፡ ዘወንጌል፡ አፍላግ፡ አዕጹቀ፡ ዘይት፡ ወዘወይን፡ ኃረግ፨</q> is added on <locus target="#16r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                        <locus from="16v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1693John"/> 3:1-8</title>
                        <note>
                           The praise <q xml:lang="gez">ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፨ ኮከብ፡ ሰመይናከ፡ ፀሓየ፡ ጽድቅ፡</q> is added on <locus target="#17"/>.
                        </note>
                        <!-- Cp. BAVet64, f. 26v l. 6, f. 27r l. 1 -->
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
                        <title>Praises to God</title>
                        <note>
                           The praises include a passage on the vision of Ezekiel, beginning as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ርኢክዎ፡ ይብል፡ ነቢይ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡ በላዔ፡ 
                              <choice><sic>መጻሕድት፡</sic></choice></q>.
                        </note>
                        <!-- Cp. BAVet64, f. 15r l.14 - f. 15v l. 5 -->
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13">
                        <locus from="22r"/>
                        <title>Praise to Our Lady Mary</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ በአርያም፡ በውስተ፡ ውሳጤ፡ መንጦላዕት፡
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.14">
                        <title>Excerpt from <title ref="LIT1812GospelLuke"/> 1:26-38</title>
                     </msItem>
